  "texts": [
    "By tailoring prompts to suit each agent, the system achieves a high degree of flexibility and accuracy, accommodating diverse data types and user intents.",
    "For queries managed by the RAG Agent, dynamic prompts are constructed to include contextual instructions that direct the LLM to synthesize information from text chunks retrieved from the vectorstore.",
    "This enables the model to leverage semantically similar text embeddings while remaining aligned with the specific details of the user's question.",
    "For example, when asked about the responsibilities of a contract manager, the prompt explicitly instructs the LLM to extract and summarize relevant clauses, enhancing both the relevance and precision of the response.",
    "For queries handled by the SQL Agent, dynamic prompts are designed to bridge the gap between natural language and structured queries, translating user input into precise SQL commands."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}